---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Abhin Rustagi" description="Full-stack developer with a passion for building thoughtful web experiences.">
  <section>
    <div class="container section-wrapper">
      <h1 class="section-title">About</h1>

      <div class="content text-muted">
        <div class="bio animate-in animate-in-delay-1">
          <p>
            Hi, my name is Abhin, a software engineer who loves a good challenge. In the past, I've had the opportunity to develop software across a variety of settings â€” from an innovative EdTech platform, or a creative MedTech solution, to just as a freelance agent for startups trying to find their feet making it big. Additionally, I also volunteer my time and engineering skills to help organisations fight the climate change battle.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dreaming up cool automative yet productivity and user-first ideas and making them come true is where my passion lies. I started programming in 2017, and made it my career in 2021. My roles have spanned the entire stack, from frontend to backend, and from AI to DevOps, and I have enjoyed almost every minute of it.
          </p>
          <p>
            In my spare time, I'm usually at the gym, climbing, enjoying cricket, researching new places to eat at or planning my next travel.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="skills animate-in animate-in-delay-2">
          <h2 class="section-title">Stack</h2>
          <p>Some technologies where I've spend most of my coding hours, but not limited to:</p>
          <p class="skill-list">
            React, Next.js, TypeScript, Node.js, Python, PostgreSQL, Redis,
            Tailwind CSS, Astro, Docker, AWS, Vercel
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact animate-in animate-in-delay-3">
          <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            I'm always open to interesting projects and collaborations.
            <a href="mailto:hello@abhin.dev">hello@abhin.dev</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .bio p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .skill-list {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .contact p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact a {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
